{"pid":"509ec0d40293f20c199dcbc9fa237c654f743435","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要有養過動物先有人請？ <br />\n現時人工幾多<br />\n前景如何<br />\n係咪要接觸埋蛇果類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來答左人工sorry 點解咁低人工仲留</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好你養過動物啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過有啲無養過都會請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人工係有啲低 不過想學下野<br />\n有啲online課程可以讀 當進修咁 不過應該都無咩前景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蛇我未掂過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多數診所都係主要醫貓狗 如果你做exotic嗰啲就一定要掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a201d34e2872a01624581105f5aa62ae015e78b2","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意貓定狗多d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己都養緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ed1cb27bcfe0f05cfe9633ca2e7cb20eb2fe86","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗唔洗帶護士帽？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2ab95c49d7885d1f13f5fa31af305f9985768b","tid":138270,"uid":52102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"1.點鮮成日說九人地去驗血 但每驗一次收至少七百幾<br />\n2.有次帶主人去睇 講到我隻主人就唔得又性 但個男護士就咬住支波板糖係度講野 串柒柒 係咪會對得多對到無哂感覺"},{"pid":"ada02df1a8300e97d2ad7cfec991485a4187c8a6","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.點鮮成日說九人地去驗血 但每驗一次收至少七百幾<br />\n2.有次帶主人去睇 講到我隻主人就唔得又性 但個男護士就咬住支波板糖係度講野 串柒柒 係咪會對得多對到無哂感覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為驗血可以睇下肝腎指數啊 紅白血球個啲正唔正常 但你次次驗全血定點 點解咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁係睇下條友冷唔冷血姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你係邊間睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次我眼見隻貓貓要人道毁滅 勁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到我都哭埋一份 可能係我眼淺"},{"pid":"216b1606fc5c9a4ae90dc890e865c3d2ce23bfbe","tid":138270,"uid":8722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無咩黑暗野可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我做左唔係好耐 所以都唔太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上一份點解走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為頂唔順某位醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有D醫生真係好撚臭格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8028619c1255319af4a66179e0266988ebe4a1d8","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無咩黑暗野可以分享下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我做左唔係好耐 所以都唔太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上一份點解走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為頂唔順某位醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有D醫生真係好撚臭格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\