kquote>點入行？見佢請人就去in?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊 睇到有請人就apply</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知果d AIRC澳洲獸醫護士課程讀左會唔會對搵工有幫助？定係純粹增加知識"},{"pid":"89da8fd8a3431bff3392c8fb30f7e826e9e193a2","tid":138270,"uid":79467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"呢份工最難頂同最開心係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caa2b82e47fdcbc04e931f672a110d7a8f39c3e","tid":138270,"uid":82727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b49a04fc6c999ee95596a097c821eda905573ef","tid":138270,"uid":80761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:26:41.000Z","msg":"有冇話要咩條件先可以做？<br />\n人工最高可以去到幾多？<br />\n有冇機會由獸醫護士升上獸醫？"},{"pid":"d490f13eb103176f1d62d85715ab782b2f70c701","tid":138270,"uid":82727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:32:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21fc81e7d11e5055b12ec258df00b52213ee3479","tid":138270,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:43:59.000Z","msg":"I hope you like animals because I am a beast."},{"pid":"e3d1fd94faee6c2b85f18056976fef237c24ada3","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點入行？見佢請人就去in?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊 睇到有請人就apply</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知果d AIRC澳洲獸醫護士課程讀左會唔會對搵工有幫助？定係純粹增加知識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都以為要讀 其實無讀都請 最緊要唔怕辛苦<br />\n你可以做做當進修咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34e5989b7c430f6a3981a1a93fa0fa4d08de0c2","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢份工最難頂同最開心係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最難頂係時不時會受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最開心我覺得係可以見到啲狗仔貓仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a320c5187474a5c7116c68ba2fe47d1a47e4e6d9","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地d獸醫護士係咪放左工就算？乜都唔理，寵物唔當係生命，做野求求其其，為左hea 可以令到一個生命疏忽導致死亡，到最後仲覺得自己冇錯，話自己係專業資格 依個係專業判斷？做獸醫護士係咪要冷血既人先做到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  首先我唔冷血 寵物係我地嘅屋企人 所以點解會唔係生命？ <br />\n我無導致過死亡 其他人我唔知 因為我返都係非24小時 所以有時可能會有動物係收左工之後嘅時間走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb75da0cc876eec8903439bd1b20e07f4745983","tid":138270,"uid":41425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"有無話讀咩課程入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab8edd71b0dbec82977f005899343783690431f","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇話要咩條件先可以做？<br />\n人工最高可以去到幾多？<br />\n有冇機會由獸醫護士升上獸醫？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩條件 我覺得真係唔怕辛苦就做到 你睇下返邊間 如果係外國醫生就一定要英文好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人工我暫時係最低個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我估16k最高掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定無機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61301c791ad521db30a97fd183d3beca7deab893","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有我想問 根據你既經驗 平時d獸醫係咪好鐘意當人地寵物係垃圾咁處理？點解危險期未過既寵物都可以求其放係一邊，簽左份野 講明要係氧氣箱過成晚 ，點知第二日隻寵物死係個籠到，而唔係氧氣箱到，咁樣其實係咩一回事？依個係咪專業判斷？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我返過幾間 見過有啲好盡責 好緊張啲動物；有啲就好粗魯對待動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係佢地見到動物係氧氣箱度走左 所以搬入個籠？<br />\n我唔敢亂批評人地 我做左無幾耐唔專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9a795676406f999bb1fc1ca4b95ea9886dfc64","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I hope you like animals because I am a beast.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> But I am not Belle"},{"pid":"329e220cc79359e85498c5427041f8c63692eaa2","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無話讀咩課程入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無啊 之前我同佢地講 其實佢地都話唔洗讀 唔好嘥錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881df9645f38f964011a7c7cb949613968ab0a59","tid":138270,"uid":83853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"見過d咩奇怪寵物名？"},{"pid":"90ea2a8396f8fd996cc70c07b17d9e2a61aa1188","tid":138270,"uid":89757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過d咩奇怪寵物名？</blockquote><br />\n有冇叫旺財既貓<br />\n或者叫喵喵既狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae8899db77b9cc444d74ed5de9e6e2fb503cbef","tid":138270,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見過d咩奇怪寵物名？</blockquote><br />\n有冇叫旺財既貓<br />\n或者叫喵喵既狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無印象見過呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見過有隻叫森美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"